definition: (emphatic sentence-final particle, used instead of 啊[a5] after a word ending in "n")
which? (interrogative, followed by classifier or numeral-classifier)
classifier indicating a small amount or small number greater than 1: some, a few, several

sentences.english: What happens in disputes between direct buyer and seller?
sentences.chinese: 直接购买者与出售者之间发生哪些争端？

sentences.english: Steven Kennard:What are the requirements for ABP choosing international partners?
sentences.chinese: 总部基地在全球选择合作伙伴都有哪些要求？

sentences.english: What publications will be published during the Guangzhou Asian Games?
sentences.chinese: 广州亚运会赛时官方出版物计划有哪些？

sentences.english: Which kind of resources are used in Biomass energy projects?
sentences.chinese: 生物质能项目中会用到哪些资源？

sentences.english: Which things are duty-free when passing through the Customs?
sentences.chinese: 哪些东西通过海关时免税？

sentences.english: You can specify which non-key columns to include in the index and use the arrows again to specify the order.
sentences.chinese: 可以指定索引中包含哪些非键列并用箭头指定次序。

sentences.english: So what about sports? What kind of sports do Thai delegation expect gold from?
sentences.chinese: 那么运动方面，哪些运动是泰国队希望夺金的呢？

sentences.english: What are the reasons to influence the turbot market?
sentences.chinese: 影响大菱鲆市场的原因有哪些？

sentences.english: What are some of the things worth avoiding?
Will there be time for a question-and-answer segment?If so, anticipate the questions and prepare responses in advance, Ms. Blackman said.
sentences.chinese: 如果是，那么期待会问哪些问题并之前准备回应。

sentences.english: Volleying is the basic skill of the game.
sentences.chinese: 网球运动员个人的基本技术有哪些？

sentences.english: Sometimes you can almost see the plan.
sentences.chinese: 有时候，你似乎可以知道哪些冥冥之中的注定。

sentences.english: Which areas of the site are they visiting before they make a purchase?
sentences.chinese: 他们在做出购买之前访问了站点的哪些区域？

sentences.english: Yeah, do you know what type of people often come to visit Yangmingshan these days?
sentences.chinese: 嗯，你猜现在经常来阳明山的是哪些人？

sentences.english: Which traffic offences will result in Driving Offence Points?
sentences.chinese: 哪些交通违章会导致违章分数的记录呢？

sentences.english: What high-level exchanges have you had recently?
sentences.chinese: 双方最近有哪些高层交往？

definition: (before a noun) Do (you, they etc) have ...?/Is there a ...?/(before a verb) Did (you, they etc) (verb, infinitive)?/Have (you, they etc) (verb, past participle)?

particle indicating that a previously asked question is to be applied to the preceding word ("What about ...?", "And ...?")/particle for inquiring about location ("Where is ...?")/particle signaling a pause, to emphasize the preceding words and allow the listener time to take them on board ("ok?", "are you with me?")/(at the end of a declarative sentence) particle indicating continuation of a state or action/particle indicating strong affirmation
to go to the bottom of a matter/after all/when all is said and done/(in an interrogative sentence) finally/outcome/result
finally/in the end/when all is said and done/after all/to the end/to the last
(used for abstract things) a good deal, a lot of
to take a look at/to examine/to survey/(coll.) pretty soon
some/a few/a little/(following an adjective) slightly ...er
